WEBVTT

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:30.959
Xin Ge.

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:33.040
Sunlight on Incense Burner brews purple mist.

00:01:33.239 --> 00:01:34.480
Cards and drinks, Xin Ge?

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:37.959
No time for cards. No golf either.

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:43.719
Same as usual. Four hundred thousand.

00:01:44.079 --> 00:01:44.680
Got it.

00:02:27.319 --> 00:02:28.240
You want in?

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:29.800
No.

00:02:31.719 --> 00:02:32.639
Place the order.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.199
Zhao Ge.

00:02:46.759 --> 00:02:47.800
How long's he been in there?

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:53.759
Hold on.

00:02:53.919 --> 00:02:54.599
Let's go check.

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.000
A Xin.

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.439
What are you doing?

00:03:25.879 --> 00:03:27.120
The zipper's stuck again.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:32.199
You should've replaced that junk ages ago.

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:34.039
Next time I'll get you a leather one.

00:03:34.719 --> 00:03:36.439
Isn't leather even heavier?

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:01.120
Feng Zhan.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:02.319
How's it going?

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:04.240
Getting used to life in Hong Kong, China?

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:05.800
Old Luo, don't even get me started.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.039
Seriously, these guys in Hong Kong, China

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.840
can drink way more than us.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:11.120
Been here days, haven't talked business.

00:04:11.199 --> 00:04:13.199
Just drinking, drinking, drinking.

00:04:14.919 --> 00:04:17.240
About what you mentioned a few days ago,

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:18.560
buying into the new company.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.439
Right, right.

00:04:19.639 --> 00:04:21.279
How's it going with your contacts there?

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:22.560
I've been waiting on your word.

00:04:23.079 --> 00:04:24.240
I was just about to bring that up.

00:04:25.279 --> 00:04:27.279
You remember Dr. Li from our team, right?

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:29.079
Earlier on,

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:31.160
he connected me with overseas investors.

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:33.000
All overseas Chinese.

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:35.680
Now they hear this project's going live,

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:36.879
they want in like you,

00:04:37.319 --> 00:04:38.560
to grab some of the original shares.

00:04:39.319 --> 00:04:40.560
Only thing is,

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:43.120
the paperwork for overseas funding

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:44.439
is just way too complicated.

00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:46.839
And I'm swamped on my end.

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:49.160
I really can't get away.

00:04:49.439 --> 00:04:50.720
No, no, don't say you can't get away.

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.360
You, you...

00:04:51.439 --> 00:04:52.519
How much are they investing?

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:54.920
Should be...

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:57.680
should be in the hundred-million range.

00:04:58.720 --> 00:04:59.800
But rest assured on one thing.

00:04:59.879 --> 00:05:01.959
I won't shortchange you on your cut.

00:05:03.319 --> 00:05:04.480
Here's what I wanted to say.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.879
Aren't you working in Hong Kong, China?

00:05:08.279 --> 00:05:10.680
Registering an SPV there is super easy.

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:12.399
So how about

00:05:12.959 --> 00:05:15.160
registering a company under your name?

00:05:15.319 --> 00:05:17.319
Just call it a bridge for the client.

00:05:17.879 --> 00:05:19.279
Once the overseas funds come in,

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:21.000
the company's equity structure

00:05:21.199 --> 00:05:22.319
will also be under your name.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:23.720
What do you think?

00:05:23.839 --> 00:05:24.560
No problem.

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:27.279
Leave it to me, old classmate.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:29.040
You focus on the law firm's business.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:31.639
I'll sort out the funding channel for you.

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:32.680
It's a deal then.

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:37.000
We'll discuss the details when you return.

00:05:37.079 --> 00:05:38.519
Sure, sure, we'll talk later.

00:05:38.879 --> 00:05:39.399
Got it.

00:06:09.480 --> 00:06:10.240
Hello, Finance Department.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:12.360
Prepare Rongpin's first payout for today.

00:06:28.399 --> 00:06:29.160
Take a look at this.

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.160
How many days haven't you slept?

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:57.319
You look so worn out.

00:06:59.040 --> 00:07:01.639
I'm sure my guess is right.

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:03.920
How is there no lead at all?

00:07:08.959 --> 00:07:09.720
Luo Xiao's law firm

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:11.720
recently set up a tech company.

00:07:13.839 --> 00:07:15.199
Got a ten-million loan from the bank.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.800
On the surface, this company

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:19.600
has no connection to Luo Xiao at all.

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:22.000
And all procedures are completely legal.

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.439
Luo Xiao again. I swear.

00:07:26.839 --> 00:07:29.560
Why would a law firm dabble in tech?

00:07:29.959 --> 00:07:31.040
That's exactly the issue.

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.439
From public records, we found

00:07:33.439 --> 00:07:35.959
this firm drew lots of overseas funding.

00:07:36.439 --> 00:07:38.040
Each one is in the tens of millions.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:42.279
You think he's laundering money.

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:45.319
But there's no evidence.

00:07:48.879 --> 00:07:50.600
Ultimately, it's all about money.

00:07:50.959 --> 00:07:51.560
Right?

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:53.439
If we find that underground bank,

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:55.079
everything else falls into place.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:59.839
The underground bank is our key evidence.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:01.279
Go home and get some rest.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:03.319
Burning out won't crack any leads.

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:17.839
Why is this Luo Xiao everywhere?

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:20.680
I almost forgot.

00:08:21.519 --> 00:08:22.439
My little niece,

00:08:22.519 --> 00:08:24.040
transferred from the provincial hospital.

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:30.920
Experimental treatment.

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:34.159
Turn around up ahead.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.080
We're going to the county hospital.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:36.559
Turn around, turn around.

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:46.399
With standard treatment,

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.159
this patient shouldn't have

00:08:48.159 --> 00:08:49.720
such a good response.

00:08:50.799 --> 00:08:52.600
Wait, what's that medicine she's taking?

00:08:52.639 --> 00:08:53.360
Veliparib.

00:08:53.519 --> 00:08:54.360
Right, Veliparib.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:56.440
Veliparib.

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:58.159
I've never heard of it being

00:08:58.159 --> 00:08:59.879
used to treat blood disorders.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:01.840
Is it some new kind of drug?

00:09:02.039 --> 00:09:02.799
Let me check.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:09.440
It's a PARP inhibitor.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.840
It's in clinical trials abroad,

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:14.360
mainly targeting some rare conditions.

00:09:14.759 --> 00:09:16.639
But for now, this kind of drug

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.480
hasn't been introduced domestically yet.

00:09:20.279 --> 00:09:22.279
For the blood disease she has,

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:24.720
there was a little girl recently

00:09:24.759 --> 00:09:25.879
with the same condition.

00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:26.960
But based on

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:29.240
our current domestic treatment standards,

00:09:29.639 --> 00:09:31.679
it's very difficult, and very expensive.

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:34.600
So basically, what you mean is,

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:38.200
this drug is still banned domestically,

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.360
right?

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:40.600
That's right.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.080
Go investigate immediately.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.600
Citywide, even province-wide,

00:09:44.039 --> 00:09:45.879
every record of Veliparib imports.

00:09:46.279 --> 00:09:46.919
Understood.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.559
Slow down.

00:10:14.360 --> 00:10:15.080
Pao.

00:10:17.639 --> 00:10:18.720
May I sit here?

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.240
She's still so young.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:33.000
This hospital has a high recovery rate.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:34.679
Don't worry too much.

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:41.879
A while back,

00:10:42.399 --> 00:10:43.440
we just moved in.

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:46.000
The doctor told us about her condition too.

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:49.679
Seeing how she's doing,

00:10:50.039 --> 00:10:52.480
I really don't feel as worried.

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:57.840
By the way,

00:10:58.679 --> 00:11:00.080
how's your husband doing?

00:11:03.639 --> 00:11:04.879
Him? Well...

00:11:06.279 --> 00:11:08.919
He's changed a lot since she got sick.

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:11.559
We fought a lot, and he was rarely home.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:13.960
Paopao.

00:11:14.519 --> 00:11:15.919
I told you not to play with that.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.080
Come, let me see your hand.

00:11:19.399 --> 00:11:20.039
Hold her.

00:11:22.559 --> 00:11:25.039
We'll head back then.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.279
Did you hurt your hand? Let me see.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.320
No.

00:11:44.639 --> 00:11:45.279
Godfather.

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:47.399
We found this.

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:52.080
Where did you find it?

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:53.639
Over there in the corner.

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:56.600
Call them all over here.

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:58.240
Everyone, come over.

00:11:59.200 --> 00:11:59.879
Come here.

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:22.159
In this room,

00:12:23.559 --> 00:12:25.559
something appeared that shouldn't be here.

00:12:25.919 --> 00:12:27.360
You've been with me for so many years,

00:12:28.159 --> 00:12:29.120
you should know

00:12:29.879 --> 00:12:31.279
what I hate the most.

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:35.159
I treat you all like my own children,

00:12:35.919 --> 00:12:38.440
so I'm willing to give you one chance.

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:41.720
Speak.

00:12:42.879 --> 00:12:43.759
Whose is this?

00:12:49.639 --> 00:12:50.360
None of ours.

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.080
Open it.

00:12:58.919 --> 00:12:59.519
A Xin.

00:13:00.279 --> 00:13:01.039
What are you doing?

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.440
The first recording

00:13:03.559 --> 00:13:04.919
was from before A Xin's incident.

00:13:08.559 --> 00:13:10.039
A Xin has an older sister, doesn't he?

00:13:26.279 --> 00:13:27.639
Send someone to keep an eye on her.

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:28.759
Yes, sir.